import React from 'react';
import {
  Button,
  Col,
  Container,
  Form,
  Modal,
  Row,
  Dropdown,
} from 'react-bootstrap';
import { landingIcons } from '../assets/icons/all';
export default function Landing() {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Row>Welcome to Homehub 1.0 !</Row>
      <Row>
        <Col>
          <Row>
            <landingIcons.one />
            What is HomeHub?
          </Row>
          <Row>
            Homehub connects students with their peers within UCSD, to create a
            reliable housing network for college students to find great places
            to live.
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <landingIcons.housing />
          </Row>
        </Col>
        <Col>
          <Row>
            <landingIcons.two />
            Why use HomeHub?
          </Row>
          <Row>
              <Col>
              <landingIcons.housing />
              </Col>
          </Row>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  );
}
